high_descs: Go forward, then turn right, then turn right again to face the table.
Pick up the spatula on the table, next to the plate.
Turn right, move forward, then turn right to face the oven.
Put the spatula in the pot on the left front corner of the oven.
Pick up the pot with the spatula in it.
Turn around, go forward, then turn left to face the table.
Put the pot on the table, to the left of the vase.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a spatula in it on the table.

high_descs: Move to the island to the right of the stove
Pick up a spatula from the island
Move to the stove to the right of you
Place the spatula in a pot on the stove
Pick up the pot with the spatula from the stove
Move to the island across from the sink
Place the pot on the island
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a spatula on the island.

high_descs: Walk to the stove then turn right and walk until you're by the green table then turn right to face it.
Pick up the spatula to the right of the plate.
Walk back to the stove and face it.
Put the spatula in the pan on the bottom left burner.
Pick up the pan with the spatula in it.
Turn around and walk until you're even with the salt shaker on the table to your left and then turn left and walk to the table.
Put the pan on the left edge of the table to the left of a weird object.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a spatula in it on the table.
